Hello Delphi,

This year The Children of the Swamp have decided to make publicly available our offseason projects discord:

Discord Link

We will be working on a new driver station, robot cart, and of course our offseason robot, Tacodile. Members of the discord will be able to sit in on our meetings and Cad streams for these projects as well as ask questions and receive the same updates the team members will for these projects.

Feel free to ask questions here or within the discord.

We look forward to seeing everyone who wants to join us this offseason!
